message.entry: Numeric or logical matrix required for image CData.
Indexed CData must be size m-by-n. TrueColor CData must be size m-by-n-by-3.
TrueColor CData contains element out of range 0.0 <= value <= 1.0.
Dimensions of AlphaData must be 1x1, or must match CData.
Image X and Y must be vectors.
Color data must be an m-by-n-by-3 or m-by-n matrix.
Color data must be numeric or logical values.
Complex values are not supported. Specify the color data as numeric or logical values.
Image TrueColor CData out of range.
Image XData and YData must be vectors.
